Package Addresses

Class domainAddress

java.lang.Object
Addresses.Address
Addresses.domainAddress
Direct Known Subclasses:
EmailAddress, WebPageAddress
public class domainAddress
extends Address
This class is used to store and handle the attributes and methods concerning the domain address/website of the clinics.
